text.paragraph:
Efficacy of oseltamivir phosphate capsules for the treatment or prophylaxis of influenza has not been established in immunocompromised patients [see Clinical Studies (14.2)
                           ]. Safety of oseltamivir phosphate capsules has been demonstrated for up to 12 weeks for prophylaxis of influenza in immunocompromised patients [see Adverse Reactions (6.1)
                           ].
